{"tid":2109682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.3旺角清場案 片證被告遭棍毆多下 速龍自稱倒地：有段時間唔知咩事","createTime":"2020-07-15T11:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T11:56:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"32fe54d83706be5c19787aa18814155868e9f783","tid":2109682,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075510&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=5ef9a24b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075510&h=d186be83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075510</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）去年8月3日的「旺角再遊行」，入夜後有大批示威者於旺角區設置路障，9人被控非法集結罪，今日（15日）在九龍城裁判法院續審。負責制服其中一名被告的「速龍」今作供，他承認曾用警棍打被捕人的手一下。呈堂片段顯示數名速龍棍毆被告多下，但作供「速龍」僅稱「我跌咗落地下，有段時間唔知咩事。」"},{"pid":"275c6594bbdaa33c03255cb7bbc1efc6bd28cc7f","tid":2109682,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b01d5b0cf1ef0da4223e6f344e1cf89c40c77f9","tid":2109682,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275c6594bbdaa33c03255cb7bbc1efc6bd28cc7f","tid":2109682,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\